3f36cc329b449331a3f8589656276535 (00:00): Life's too short to live that way, spent too long that way myself :-(

e490b727c0dd7f2d225aea0911b7f79a (00:01): well, you see, stranger, i need something to make me smile.
e490b727c0dd7f2d225aea0911b7f79a (00:02): sometimes i just sit and look at how i am..
e490b727c0dd7f2d225aea0911b7f79a (00:02): it's just not cool.
e490b727c0dd7f2d225aea0911b7f79a (00:02): i haven't used my computer for two weeks, just cause i don't like sitting and doing nothing.
e490b727c0dd7f2d225aea0911b7f79a (00:02): but seems like i always end up on here.
e490b727c0dd7f2d225aea0911b7f79a (00:02): where nobody believes i'm a girl. u.u
3f36cc329b449331a3f8589656276535 (00:03): I understand. Our technology is more seductive every day... more seductive than we are sometimes. Sadly.
3f36cc329b449331a3f8589656276535 (00:03): why don't you like to look at yourself?
e490b727c0dd7f2d225aea0911b7f79a (00:03): haha, more seductive than we are.
e490b727c0dd7f2d225aea0911b7f79a (00:03): not physically, but generally.
e490b727c0dd7f2d225aea0911b7f79a (00:04): my life and what i've done.
e490b727c0dd7f2d225aea0911b7f79a (00:04): i'm not that old, but still.. i could be doing better.
3f36cc329b449331a3f8589656276535 (00:04): well that's good. I always feel better when I'm talking to a sexy woman like yourself.
3f36cc329b449331a3f8589656276535 (00:04): That is a dangerous place to go.
3f36cc329b449331a3f8589656276535 (00:04): Thoughts like that don't lead to good places, I know.
3f36cc329b449331a3f8589656276535 (00:05): When is the last time you just let yourself have fun? Not get drunk pass out fun, but walk through a park and stare at the clouds fun?
e490b727c0dd7f2d225aea0911b7f79a (00:05): a really long time ago..
3f36cc329b449331a3f8589656276535 (00:06): Sunsets. Sunrises. I love looking at them. All different. Never happening again. Like us.
e490b727c0dd7f2d225aea0911b7f79a (00:06): that's nice.
e490b727c0dd7f2d225aea0911b7f79a (00:06): i like the stars and the moon.
3f36cc329b449331a3f8589656276535 (00:07): I had a gf once, she had a sun tattooed above one breast, the moon above the other. Pale colors, bluish black. Dragon on her back.
3f36cc329b449331a3f8589656276535 (00:07): We ran once, on the beach of North Carolina, while she was half drunk riding piggy back through the sand
3f36cc329b449331a3f8589656276535 (00:08): She asked me if the reason I liked to carry her was to feel her pussy on my back. I told her no. Made me sad.
e490b727c0dd7f2d225aea0911b7f79a (00:08): interesting.
e490b727c0dd7f2d225aea0911b7f79a (00:09): so why did you like carrying her around?
3f36cc329b449331a3f8589656276535 (00:09): It made her laugh. For a moment it made her forget and enjoy the moment.
3f36cc329b449331a3f8589656276535 (00:09): Not all the time, sometimes though.
3f36cc329b449331a3f8589656276535 (00:10): I still think of her every now and then, we all have our moments.
3f36cc329b449331a3f8589656276535 (00:10): She's been married three years now.
3f36cc329b449331a3f8589656276535 (00:11): your turn.... a memory.... a happy one...
